{
  "id": "RAW_74725940",
  "title": "Gemini е…Ҳиҝӣзҝ»иҜ‘иғҪеҠӣиөӢиғҪ Google зҝ»иҜ‘",
  "url": "https://blog.google/products/search/gemini-capabilities-translation-upgrades/",
  "date": "2025-12-12 17:02:37",
  "author": "Rose Yao",
  "siteName": "The Keyword (blog.google) ",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <uni-article-speakable style=\"height: 55px; margin-bottom: 36px; display: block;\" page-title=\"Bringing state\\u002Dof\\u002Dthe\\u002Dart Gemini translation capabilities to Google Translate\" listen-to-article=\"Listen to article\" data-date-modified=\"2025-12-12T17:02:37.681749+00:00\" data-tracking-ids=\"G-HGNBTNCHCQ,G-6NKTLKV14N\" data-voice-list=\"en.ioh-pngnat:Cyan,en.usb-pngnat:Lime\" data-script-src=\"https://www.gstatic.com/readaloud/player/web/api/js/api.js\" data-highlight-mode=\"word-over-paragraph\">\n   <!---->\n   <div id=\"uni-article-speakable\">\n    <!--?lit$82033432$-->\n    <span width=\"14px\"> \n     <svg width=\"24px\" viewBox=\"0 0 66 66\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" class=\"uni-spinner uni-spinner--small\">\n      <circle class=\"loader-path\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"7\" cx=\"33\" cy=\"33\" r=\"25\"></circle>\n     </svg> \n    </span>\n   </div>\n  </uni-article-speakable>\n  <!--article text-->\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Bringing state\\u002Dof\\u002Dthe\\u002Dart Gemini translation capabilities to Google Translate&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"m1fv5\" class=\"drop-cap\">True understanding comes from not just <i>what</i> someone says, but also the nuance of <i>how</i> they say it. Today, Google Translate is getting better at both.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"20tnk\">WeвҖҷre introducing state-of-the-art text translation quality <a class=\"superscript\" data-ga4-analytics-superscript-click=\"\" data-target=\"inline text\" href=\"#footnote-1\" id=\"footnote-source-1\" aria-label=\"Jump to link reference 1\"> <sup>1</sup> </a> in Search and the Translate app, built with Gemini. This means youвҖҷll get much smarter, more natural and accurate text translations wherever youвҖҷre searching. WeвҖҷre also rolling out a new beta version of live translation, that brings real-time, natural-sounding translations right to your headphones with the help of <a href=\"https://blog.google/products/gemini/gemini-audio-model-updates/\">GeminiвҖҷs new, native speech-to-speech translation capabilities</a>. Plus, weвҖҷre adding more languages for you to practice in the Translate app.</p>\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"b6o8i\">Get smarter, more natural translations, built with Gemini</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"2ieaj\">Starting today, Google Translate uses advanced Gemini capabilities to better improve translations on phrases with more nuanced meanings like idioms, local expressions or slang.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"eeb70\">Say youвҖҷre trying to translate an English idiom like вҖң<i>stealing my thunder</i>.вҖқ Now, it's easier than ever to get a more natural, accurate translation, instead of a literal word-for-word translation. Gemini parses the context to give you a helpful translation that captures what the idiom really means.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-image-full-width alignment=\"large\" alt-text=\"A smartphone displays a Google Search result with a prominent Google Translate box. The English sentence &quot;he announced it right before me and really stole my thunder&quot; is translated into Spanish as &quot;lo anunciГі justo antes que yo y me robГі todo el protagonismo&quot;. The interface includes language selection dropdowns, audio icons for both languages, and standard Google mobile search elements like the search bar, navigation icons, and other results below.\" external-image=\"\" or-mp4-video-title=\"\" or-mp4-video-url=\"\" section-header=\"Bringing state\\u002Dof\\u002Dthe\\u002Dart Gemini translation capabilities to Google Translate\" custom-class=\"image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"image-full-width image-full-width--large image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Inline Images&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;Bringing state\\\\u002Dof\\\\u002Dthe\\\\u002Dart Gemini translation capabilities to Google Translate&quot;}\">\n    <!--?lit$82033432$-->\n    <!--?lit$82033432$-->\n    <div class=\" image-full-width__media-asset \">\n     <!--?lit$82033432$-->\n     <div slot=\"image-slot\" style=\"display: block;\">\n      <img alt=\"A smartphone displays a Google Search result with a prominent Google Translate box. The English sentence &quot;he announced it right before me and really stole my thunder&quot; is translated into Spanish as &quot;lo anunciГі justo antes que yo y me robГі todo el protagonismo&quot;. The interface includes language selection dropdowns, audio icons for both languages, and standard Google mobile search elements like the search bar, navigation icons, and other results below.\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Asset-1_Text-Translations-with-Ge.width-100.format-webp.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" data-loading=\"{\n            &quot;mobile&quot;: &quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Asset-1_Text-Translations-with-Ge.width-500.format-webp.webp&quot;,\n            &quot;desktop&quot;: &quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Asset-1_Text-Translations-with-G.width-1000.format-webp.webp&quot;\n          }\">\n     </div>\n     <!--?lit$82033432$-->\n     <!--?lit$82033432$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$82033432$-->\n     <!--?lit$82033432$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$82033432$-->\n     <!--?lit$82033432$-->\n     <!--?-->\n    </div>\n    <!--?-->\n    <!--?lit$82033432$-->\n    <!--?lit$82033432$-->\n    <!--?-->\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-full-width>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Bringing state\\u002Dof\\u002Dthe\\u002Dart Gemini translation capabilities to Google Translate&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"m1fv5\">This update is rolling out starting today in the U.S. and India translating between English and nearly 20 languages, including Spanish, Hindi, Chinese, Japanese and German, in the Translate app (<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.google.android.apps.translate\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Android</a> and <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/google-translate/id414706506\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">iOS</a>) and on the <a href=\"http://translate.google.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">web</a>.</p>\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"32bme\">Hear and understand the world in real-time</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"b79ja\">Building on <a href=\"https://blog.google/technology/developers/gemini-2-5-native-audio-updates\">GeminiвҖҷs new live speech-to-speech translation capabilities</a>, we are rolling out a beta experience enabling you to hear real-time translations in your headphones. This new experience works to preserve the tone, emphasis and cadence of each speaker to create more natural translations and make it easier to follow along with who said what. Whether you're trying to have a conversation in a different language, listen to a speech or lecture while abroad, or watch a TV show or film in another language, you can now put in your headphones, open the Translate app, tap вҖңLive translateвҖқ and hear a real-time translation in your preferred language.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-youtube-player-article index=\"4\" thumbnail-alt=\"A smartphone is shown, as a user opens the Translate app, taps &quot;live translate&quot; and inputs headphones as part of the beta speech-to-speech experience. A male and female speaker give a toast in a wedding in Spanish and you see the English translation and hear it with the same cadence, tone and emphasis of the speakers natural voices.\" video-id=\"6F3oGXf8dfM\" video-type=\"video\" is-short=\"true\">\n   <!---->\n   <div data-yt-video=\"module\" class=\"article-video-special h-c-page--mobile-full-bleed article-video--shorts\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Youtube Video&quot;}\">\n    <div class=\"article-video-special__container\">\n     <div class=\"article-module uni-article-video uni-article-video--body\" data-component=\"uni-article-yt-player\" data-page-title=\"\" data-video-id=\"6F3oGXf8dfM\" data-index-id=\"4\" data-type=\"video\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n      <button class=\"h-c-video h-c-video--marquee uni-article-video__custom-wrapper\" tabindex=\"0\">\n       <div class=\"uni-article-video__aspect-image\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/6F3oGXf8dfM/default.webp\" alt=\"A smartphone is shown, as a user opens the Translate app, taps &quot;live translate&quot; and inputs headphones as part of the beta speech-to-speech experience. A male and female speaker give a toast in a wedding in Spanish and you see the English translation and hear it with the same cadence, tone and emphasis of the speakers natural voices.\" data-loading=\"{\n                    &quot;desktop&quot;: &quot;https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/6F3oGXf8dfM/sddefault.webp&quot;,\n                    &quot;mobile&quot;: &quot;https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/6F3oGXf8dfM/mqdefault.webp&quot;\n                  }\"><uni-icon-component class=\"uni-article-video__icon-wrapper\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__play-button--active\" remove-viewbox=\"true\" icon-id=\"yt_video_shorts_play_button_no_hole\"><!----></uni-icon-component><uni-icon-component class=\"uni-article-video__icon-wrapper\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__play-button\" custom-role=\"img\" remove-viewbox=\"true\" icon-id=\"yt_video_shorts_play_button\" custom-label=\"Video Title \"><!----></uni-icon-component><!--?lit$82033432$-->\n       </div>\n      </button>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </uni-youtube-player-article>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Bringing state\\u002Dof\\u002Dthe\\u002Dart Gemini translation capabilities to Google Translate&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"m1fv5\">Following positive feedback in early testing, we're excited to make this beta more broadly available to collect even more feedback as we work to refine the model and experience. Starting today the beta is rolling out in the Translate app on Android in the U.S., Mexico, and India, works with any pair of headphones, and supports more than <a href=\"https://support.google.com/translate/answer/6142474?hl=en&amp;co=GENIE.Platform%3DAndroid\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">70 languages</a>. And weвҖҷll be bringing it to iOS and more countries in 2026. Try it out in the Android app and let us know your thoughts via <a href=\"https://support.google.com/translate/answer/6142474?hl=en&amp;co=GENIE.Platform%3DAndroid\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">in-app feedback</a>!</p>\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"1653q\">Practice and master even more languages in Translate</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"8knq\">Starting today, weвҖҷre also expanding our <a href=\"https://blog.google/products/translate/language-learning-live-translate/\">language learning</a> tools in the Translate app with improved feedback so you can get helpful tips based on your speaking practice. WeвҖҷre also introducing a way for you to challenge yourself and reach your learning goals by tracking how many days in a row youвҖҷve been learning, so you can clearly see your progress and consistency over time.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-image-full-width alignment=\"full\" alt-text=\"The Google Translate app is shown in a phone and displays the app's displaying a speaking practice tool. interface. The screen confirms &quot;You earned a daily activity star!&quot; with a speaking score of 3 out of 5. At the bottom, a pop-up card celebrates a milestone as a lightning bolt icon animates and the text increments from a &quot;3&quot; to a &quot;4 day streak.&quot; A row of days below the number highlights the current progress with blue lightning bolts.\" external-image=\"\" or-mp4-video-title=\"Translate app language practice streak\" or-mp4-video-url=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Asset_4b_DailyStreak_1080x1080_v1.mp4\" section-header=\"Bringing state\\u002Dof\\u002Dthe\\u002Dart Gemini translation capabilities to Google Translate\" custom-class=\"image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"image-full-width image-full-width--full image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Inline Images&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;Bringing state\\\\u002Dof\\\\u002Dthe\\\\u002Dart Gemini translation capabilities to Google Translate&quot;}\">\n    <!--?lit$82033432$-->\n    <!--?lit$82033432$-->\n    <div class=\" image-full-width__media-asset image-full-width__media-asset--mp4 \">\n     <!--?lit$82033432$-->\n     <!--?lit$82033432$-->\n     <!--?lit$82033432$-->\n     <video autoplay=\"\" loop=\"\" muted playsinline=\"\" type=\"video/mp4\" aria-label=\"The Google Translate app is shown in a phone and displays the app's displaying a speaking practice tool. interface. The screen confirms &quot;You earned a daily activity star!&quot; with a speaking score of 3 out of 5. At the bottom, a pop-up card celebrates a milestone as a lightning bolt icon animates and the text increments from a &quot;3&quot; to a &quot;4 day streak.&quot; A row of days below the number highlights the current progress with blue lightning bolts.\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Asset_4b_DailyStreak_1080x1080_v1.mp4\">\n      Sorry, your browser doesn't support embedded videos, but don't worry, you can <a href=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Asset_4b_DailyStreak_1080x1080_v1.mp4\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">download it</a> and watch it with your favorite video player!\n     </video>\n     <!--?lit$82033432$-->\n     <!--?lit$82033432$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$82033432$-->\n     <!--?lit$82033432$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$82033432$-->\n     <!--?lit$82033432$-->\n     <!--?-->\n    </div>\n    <!--?-->\n    <!--?lit$82033432$-->\n    <!--?lit$82033432$-->\n    <!--?-->\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-full-width>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Bringing state\\u002Dof\\u002Dthe\\u002Dart Gemini translation capabilities to Google Translate&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"m1fv5\">And weвҖҷre expanding the capability to nearly 20 new countries including Germany, India, Sweden, and Taiwan, so even more people can continue to refine their language skills, including:</p>\n     <ul>\n      <li data-block-key=\"94ki1\">English to German and Portuguese</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"ctr42\">Bengali, Mandarin Chinese (Simplified), Dutch, German, Hindi, Italian, Romanian, and Swedish to English</li>\n     </ul>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-image-full-width alignment=\"full\" alt-text=\"The Google Translate app is shown on a phone screen. Two side-by-side screens show different experiences of the language learning tool. The left screen says &quot;Practice German&quot; and  shows a dashboard with the user's goal set to &quot;Get a job as a waiter,&quot; an 8-day streak, and recommended scenarios like &quot;Announcing today's specials.&quot; The right screen shows an active conversation practice session with German text prompts, such as &quot;Was wollen Sie bestellen?&quot; (What do you want to order?), accompanied by a large blue microphone button for voice input.\" external-image=\"\" or-mp4-video-title=\"\" or-mp4-video-url=\"\" section-header=\"Bringing state\\u002Dof\\u002Dthe\\u002Dart Gemini translation capabilities to Google Translate\" custom-class=\"image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"image-full-width image-full-width--full image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Inline Images&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;Bringing state\\\\u002Dof\\\\u002Dthe\\\\u002Dart Gemini translation capabilities to Google Translate&quot;}\">\n    <!--?lit$82033432$-->\n    <!--?lit$82033432$-->\n    <div class=\" image-full-width__media-asset \">\n     <!--?lit$82033432$-->\n     <div slot=\"image-slot\" style=\"display: block;\">\n      <img alt=\"The Google Translate app is shown on a phone screen. Two side-by-side screens show different experiences of the language learning tool. The left screen says &quot;Practice German&quot; and  shows a dashboard with the user's goal set to &quot;Get a job as a waiter,&quot; an 8-day streak, and recommended scenarios like &quot;Announcing today's specials.&quot; The right screen shows an active conversation practice session with German text prompts, such as &quot;Was wollen Sie bestellen?&quot; (What do you want to order?), accompanied by a large blue microphone button for voice input.\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/AI_in_Translate_inline_3.width-100.format-webp.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" data-loading=\"{\n            &quot;mobile&quot;: &quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/AI_in_Translate_inline_3.width-500.format-webp.webp&quot;,\n            &quot;desktop&quot;: &quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/AI_in_Translate_inline_3.width-1000.format-webp.webp&quot;\n          }\">\n     </div>\n     <!--?lit$82033432$-->\n     <!--?lit$82033432$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$82033432$-->\n     <!--?lit$82033432$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$82033432$-->\n     <!--?lit$82033432$-->\n     <!--?-->\n    </div>\n    <!--?-->\n    <!--?lit$82033432$-->\n    <!--?lit$82033432$-->\n    <!--?-->\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-full-width>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Bringing state\\u002Dof\\u002Dthe\\u002Dart Gemini translation capabilities to Google Translate&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"m1fv5\">WeвҖҷve heard from users that they appreciate the customized learning experiences that reflect real-life scenarios. We'll continue to add new ways for people to make progress on their language learning goals.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"5ono4\">With even more advanced AI models and expanded language learning capabilities in Translate, weвҖҷre helping you capture not just the words, but the meaning behind them. WeвҖҷre excited to <i>hear</i> what you think.<span class=\"tombstone\"></span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Google зҝ»иҜ‘ж•ҙеҗҲ Gemini зҡ„е…ҲиҝӣиғҪеҠӣпјҢжҸҗдҫӣжӣҙжҷәиғҪгҖҒжӣҙиҮӘз„¶зҡ„ж–Үжң¬е’Ңе®һж—¶иҜӯйҹізҝ»иҜ‘пјҢе№¶жү©еұ•дәҶиҜӯиЁҖеӯҰд№ еҠҹиғҪгҖӮ",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Google зҝ»иҜ‘ж•ҙеҗҲ Gemini зҡ„е…ҲиҝӣиғҪеҠӣпјҢжҸҗдҫӣжӣҙжҷәиғҪгҖҒжӣҙиҮӘз„¶зҡ„ж–Үжң¬е’Ңе®һж—¶иҜӯйҹізҝ»иҜ‘пјҢе№¶жү©еұ•дәҶиҜӯиЁҖеӯҰд№ еҠҹиғҪгҖӮ",
  "summary": "Google зҝ»иҜ‘жӯЈеңЁйҖҡиҝҮж•ҙеҗҲ Google AI жЁЎеһӢ Gemini зҡ„е…ҲиҝӣеҠҹиғҪжқҘеўһејәе…¶иғҪеҠӣгҖӮжӯӨж¬ЎеҚҮзә§жҳҫи‘—жҸҗй«ҳдәҶж–Үжң¬зҝ»иҜ‘иҙЁйҮҸпјҢзү№еҲ«жҳҜеҜ№дәҺд№ иҜӯе’ҢдҝҡиҜӯзӯүз»Ҷеҫ®зҹӯиҜӯпјҢйҖҡиҝҮеҲ©з”Ё Gemini еӨҚжқӮзҡ„дёҠдёӢж–ҮзҗҶи§ЈиғҪеҠӣпјҢиғҪжҸҗдҫӣжӣҙиҮӘз„¶гҖҒжӣҙеҮҶзЎ®зҡ„зҝ»иҜ‘гҖӮжӯӨеҠҹиғҪжңҖеҲқеңЁзҫҺеӣҪе’ҢеҚ°еәҰжҺЁеҮәпјҢж”ҜжҢҒиӢұиҜӯе’Ңиҝ‘ 20 з§Қе…¶д»–иҜӯиЁҖгҖӮжӯӨеӨ–пјҢжӯЈеңЁжҺЁеҮәе®һж—¶иҜӯйҹіеҲ°иҜӯйҹізҝ»иҜ‘зҡ„ж–° Beta зүҲпјҢе®ғеҲ©з”Ё Gemini зҡ„еҺҹз”ҹйҹійў‘жЁЎеһӢжҸҗдҫӣе®һж—¶зҝ»иҜ‘пјҢеҗҢж—¶дҝқжҢҒиҜҙиҜқиҖ…зҡ„иҜӯж°”гҖҒйҮҚйҹіе’ҢиҜӯи°ғпјҢдҪҝеҜ№иҜқе’ҢеӘ’дҪ“ж¶Ҳиҙ№жӣҙиҮӘз„¶гҖҒжӣҙе®№жҳ“зҗҶи§ЈгҖӮжӯӨ Beta зүҲеңЁ Android и®ҫеӨҮдёҠдәҺзҫҺеӣҪгҖҒеўЁиҘҝе“Ҙе’ҢеҚ°еәҰеҸҜз”ЁпјҢж”ҜжҢҒ 70 еӨҡз§ҚиҜӯиЁҖгҖӮжңҖеҗҺпјҢзҝ»иҜ‘еә”з”ЁжӯЈеңЁжү©еұ•е…¶иҜӯиЁҖеӯҰд№ е·Ҙе…·пјҢжҸҗдҫӣж”№иҝӣзҡ„еҸҚйҰҲе’ҢиҝӣеәҰи·ҹиёӘпјҢеўһеҠ дәҶеҜ№иҝ‘ 20 дёӘж–°еӣҪе®¶е’ҢжӣҙеӨҡиҜӯиЁҖеҜ№зҡ„ж”ҜжҢҒпјҢд»Ҙеё®еҠ©з”ЁжҲ·з»ғд№ е’ҢжҺҢжҸЎж–°иҜӯиЁҖгҖӮ",
  "mainPoints": [
